description:
Suika Game Planet suddenly showed up on the Nintendo eShop, so Marty and KC are going to take a look at the sequel to one of the best zone-out puzzle games in the history of humanity.

If you dig watching us play through these full series of games, considering supporting us over at Patreon -- https://www.patreon.com/SecondWindGroup

title: GOTY 2026 Has Arrived in Suika Game Planet w/ KC and Marty
